    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Representative Bauplans of the anterior ends of Stephanoceros (A, B) and Collotheca (C, D). A. Stephanoceros fimbriatus. B. Stephanoceros millsii. C. Collotheca campanulata. D. Collotheca ornata. Symbols: e = embryo; d= debris; gt = gelatinous tube; i = infundibulum; l = lobes; s = setae; t = tentacles. Bars: A, B = 500 µm C, D = 100 µm." ;
